duplicator-toolbox: Used as text for the link which is in the toolbox.
duplicator-header:
Used as header text in [[Special:Duplicator]].

Followed by the form.
duplicator-source:
Used as label for the "Source page title" inputbox.
{{Identical|Source}}
duplicator-dest:
Used as label for the "Destination page title" inputbox.
{{Identical|Destination}}
duplicator-dosubpages: Used as checkbox label. "Duplicate" is an imperative: checking the box asks for the subpages to be included in the action.
duplicator-submit:
Used as label for the Submit button.
{{Identical|Duplicate}}
duplicator-summary:
Used as a revision summary. Parameters:
* $1 - source page title
* $2 - revision ID
duplicator-success:
Used as success message.

Followed by the message {{msg-mw|Duplicator-success-revisions}}.

Parameters:
* $1 - source page title
* $2 - destination page title
duplicator-success-revisions:
Used as success message.

Preceded by the message {{msg-mw|Duplicator-success}}.

Parameters:
* $1 - number of revisions
duplicator-success-talknotcopied: Used as failure message when duplicating the talk page.
duplicator-failed-toolong:
Used as failure message. Parameters:
* $1 - source page title
See also:
* {{msg-mw|Duplicator-failed-dest-exists}}
duplicator-failed-dest-exists:
Used as failure message. Parameters:
* $1 - source page title
* $2 - destination page title
See also:
* {{msg-mw|Duplicator-failed-toolong}}
duplicator-source-notexist:
Used as error message. Parameters:
* $1 - source page title
See also:
* {{msg-mw|Duplicator-dest-exists}}
duplicator-dest-exists:
Used as error message. Parameters:
* $1 - destination page title
See also:
* {{msg-mw|Duplicator-source-notexist}}
